trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateChanged" /> or <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateSelected" /> events of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar" /> control.

The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateChanged> event occurs when the currently selected date or range of dates changes; for example, when the user explicitly changes a selection within the current month or when the selection is implicitly changed in response to next/previous month navigation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateChanged> evento ocorre quando a data atualmente selecionada ou intervalo de datas de alterações; por exemplo, quando o usuário altera explicitamente uma seleção dentro do mês atual ou implicitamente, a seleção é alterada em resposta à navegação para o mês seguinte/anterior.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateSelected> event occurs when the user explicitly changes a selection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateSelected> evento ocorre quando o usuário altera explicitamente uma seleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor specifies the start and end for the new date range that has been selected.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> construtor Especifica o início e término para o novo intervalo de datas selecionado.

trans-unit.source: If a single date is selected, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.End%2A> property values will be equal.
trans-unit.target: Se uma única data for selecionada, o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.Start%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.End%2A> os valores de propriedade serão iguais.

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling events, see [Handling and Raising Events](~/docs/standard/events/index.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre a manipulação de eventos, consulte [tratamento e gerando eventos](~/docs/standard/events/index.md).

trans-unit.source: The following example displays a form containing a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> control that displays one calendar year.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir exibe um formulário que contém um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> controle que exibe um ano.

trans-unit.source: The example demonstrates setting properties like <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BackColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ForeColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.TitleBackColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.TitleForeColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.CalendarDimensions%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.TrailingForeColor%2A> to customize the look of the calendar control.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo demonstra como definir propriedades como <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BackColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ForeColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.TitleBackColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.TitleForeColor%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.CalendarDimensions%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.TrailingForeColor%2A> para personalizar a aparência do controle de calendário.

trans-unit.source: Other properties like <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.AnnuallyBoldedDates%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.BoldedDates%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MonthlyBoldedDates%2A> are set to customize which dates are bolded.
trans-unit.target: Outras propriedades como <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.AnnuallyBoldedDates%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.BoldedDates%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MonthlyBoldedDates%2A> são definidos para personalizar quais datas estão em negrito.

trans-unit.source: The example also sets properties to change the calendar format, including <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.FirstDayOfWeek%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MaxDate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MinDate%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MaxSelectionCount%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo também define propriedades para alterar o formato de calendário, incluindo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.FirstDayOfWeek%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MaxDate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MinDate%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.MaxSelectionCount%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateSelected> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateChanged> events are also handled and their status displayed on the form.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateSelected> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.DateChanged> eventos também são manipulados e seu status é exibido no formulário.

trans-unit.source: The first date/time value in the range that the user has selected.
The last date/time value in the range that the user has selected.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs" /> class.

The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.End%2A> property values are set by the `start` and `end` parameter values of this constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.Start%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateRangeEventArgs.End%2A> valores de propriedade são definidos pelo `start` e `end` valores de parâmetro deste construtor.

trans-unit.source: Gets the last date/time value in the range that the user has selected.
A <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> that represents the last date in the date range that the user has selected.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> que representa a última data no intervalo de datas selecionado pelo usuário.
